BUILD CUMULUS


DEPENDENCIES

Source code is crossplatform, and has just two dependencies:
- POCO in its Basic Edition format (http://pocoproject.org/download/)
- Openssl (http://www.openssl.org/)

WINDOWS BUILD

You have Visual Studio 2008 file solutions and projects.

LINUX/MACOSX

Sources code and POCO are crossplatform. POCO has all makefile ready for the differents platforms.
Cumulus has not makefile for this time...




